context:
KR:
&lt;어때? 시춘이가 준비해 준 찻잎으로 끓였대. 백호은침… 이랬나?&gt;
EN:
&lt;How's the taste? Said they brewed it with the tea leaves Xichun gave us. It's called Baihao Yinzhen... or something, I think?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…그래?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Yeah?&gt;

KR:
&lt;나도 맛을 비교해 보고 싶은데… 이럴 때마다 입이 없는 게 너무 아쉽단 말이지.&gt;
EN:
&lt;As much as I'd love to be a part of that discussion... this thing didn't come with a mouth.&gt;

KR:
&lt;아, 아니 뭐… 그 정돈 아냐.&gt;
EN:
&lt;W-well, you know... it's not all that bad.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래, 고마워.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Yeah, thanks.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…무슨 일이야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... What's going on?&gt;

KR:
&lt;저건…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Is that...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;다들 괜찮은 거야…? 뭔가 대관원에 다시 습격을 온 거라던가…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Is everything okay here...? Hope it's not another attack on Daguanyuan...&gt;

KR:
&lt;…어디?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Where?&gt;

KR:
&lt;이 빛은…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hey, this light...&gt;

KR:
&lt;응? 역시라니?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Huh? What do you mean "knew it"?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…내기?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... A betting pool?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;
